00:37:30.450 --> 00:37:33.240 align:middle line:84%
to help me put one foot
back in front of the other

00:37:33.240 --> 00:37:37.250 align:middle line:84%
and get back out onto
the track of life.

00:37:37.250 --> 00:37:39.257 align:middle line:90%
>> You got lucky kids, Kim.

00:37:39.257 --> 00:37:41.340 align:middle line:84%
They're lucky to have those
messages in your life.

00:37:41.340 --> 00:37:42.290 align:middle line:90%
Yeah, wow.

00:37:42.290 --> 00:37:44.870 align:middle line:84%
>> Well I can tell you at
