not only to ourselves,

00:43:31.430 --> 00:43:33.720 align:middle line:84%
but to each other, and
not only to each other,

00:43:33.720 --> 00:43:34.910 align:middle line:90%
but to the planet.

00:43:34.910 --> 00:43:36.710 align:middle line:84%
After all, the
vibrational frequency

00:43:36.710 --> 00:43:39.970 align:middle line:84%
that we all share with one
another is in fact all one.

00:43:39.970 --> 00:43:43.460 align:middle line:84%
And if we can only tap into
that and realize that I'm only

00:43:43.460 --> 00:43:46.050 align:middle line:84%
as powerful as you're
as powerful as me,

00:43:46.050 --> 00:43:51.320 align:middle line:84%
then a beautiful dance can
occur between other human beings

00:43:51.320 --> 00:43:55.070 align:middle line:84%
and what it means to be
truly in love with oneself.

00:43:55.070 --> 00:43:57.900 align:middle line:10%
I think that's the key.

